        "title": "Fix Feishu monitor runtime initialization",
        "body": "Fixes #88024\n\nNote: this pull request was made with AI assistance.\n\n## Summary\n- Seed bundled channel runtime setters with the full scoped plugin runtime before account startup.\n- Persist channel `origin` alongside runtime registrations in the real `createPluginRegistry` channel path, so bundled Feishu entries are detected in production registry state.\n- Add gateway, registry, and Feishu startup regression coverage for runtime seeding.\n\n## Verification\n- `docker run --rm -v /tmp/openclaw-feishu-fix:/workspace -v /tmp/openclaw-work.DNxJRE/repo/node_modules:/workspace/node_modules -w /workspace node:24-bookworm bash -lc 'corepack enable && OPENCLAW_HEAVY_CHECK_LOCK_SCOPE=worktree node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/plugins/registry.runtime-config.test.ts src/gateway/server-channels.test.ts extensions/feishu/src/monitor.startup.test.ts'` (43 tests passed)\n\n## Real behavior proof\nBehavior addressed: Feishu WebSocket monitor startup now seeds the bundled channel runtime setter from the loaded plugin runtime before account startup, so inbound handlers using `getFeishuRuntime()` do not see an uninitialized runtime.\n\nReal environment tested: Containerized OpenClaw checkout using `node:24-bookworm` with workspace dependencies installed; no live Feishu credentials.\n\nExact steps or command run after this patch: `docker run --rm -v /tmp/openclaw-feishu-fix:/workspace -v /tmp/openclaw-work.DNxJRE/repo/node_modules:/workspace/node_modules -w /workspace node:24-bookworm bash -lc 'corepack enable && OPENCLAW_HEAVY_CHECK_LOCK_SCOPE=worktree node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/plugins/registry.runtime-config.test.ts src/gateway/server-channels.test.ts extensions/feishu/src/monitor.startup.test.ts'`\n\nEvidence after fix: Terminal output copied from the container run:\n```console\nRUN v4.1.7 /workspace\n✓ extension-feishu ../../extensions/feishu/src/monitor.startup.test.ts (6 tests) 6646ms\n✓ plugins ../../src/plugins/registry.runtime-config.test.ts (3 tests) 36ms\n✓ gateway-server ../../src/gateway/server-channels.test.ts (34 tests) 27ms\nTest Files 3 passed (3)\nTests 43 passed (43)\n```\n\nObserved result after fix: The registry test proves the real `api.registerChannel` path stores `origin: \"bundled\"` with the scoped runtime registration, and the gateway test proves bundled runtime setters receive the full plugin runtime before startup.\n\nWhat was not tested: Live Feishu WebSocket delivery with real Feishu app credentials.\n",
